review_content: I have been using Too Faces Sweathearts for years and was looking for a reboot. I am so glad I went with this over Nars Orgasm. While they are almost identical in color, this does blur pores and goes on with an air brush quality. The Sweet Cheeks color can be made bold or as a hint of color. A keeper for sure!!

product_name: IT Cosmetics Bye Bye Pores Blush
user_specs: ['Eye Color Brown', 'Hair color Brunette', 'Skin Tone Medium', 'Skin Type Oily']
review_content:
I purchased this because I liked the color on me, and I was looking for something that blended a little easier than when I use my finger and my Stila cream blush. Not only was it easier to blend, but it lasts a lot longer too!! I would dot my Stila cream blush on my cheeks with my finger at 7:30 am, and by noon it would have worn off. I’d reapply at noon and again at 4 pm. Maybe it was fading because I have oily skin and I blot throughout the day. But still, this IT blush lasted all day, even with blotting! Nice!
